Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 跑哪裏去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯也沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小肥 小肥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不想待了 這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 冷靜點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(658,385)\3c&H000000&\shad0\bord2\be3}「神社與寺廟」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年是不是干梅雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一帶樹木很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是寺廟哦 春
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺廟？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都是臭小子說要去看石獅子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分抱歉 銀太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 也順便可以帶悟逛逛城鎮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌麻煩就在家裏躺著唄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也那麼想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你慢死了 快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？這聲音在哪聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:50.46,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了 好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？小真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將平同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 好大的寺廟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有 破舊不堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才是和由美打電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說對了 她說她現在要過來看小肥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們關係真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小真才是 你男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是有來往的神社家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你臉紅個什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 其他人看不見小春和銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是看在眼裏的就是我們倆單獨在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天本 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神尾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說和我們不是一個學校 他是由美的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思 剛才的停頓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是想說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 冱木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在這做什麼呀 連神尾也在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 只是帶悟逛逛城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 去看看小咪的情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧 來來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺廟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是帶禮物來 真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小將 由美來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 還有不認識的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的朋友 冱木和神尾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎 我是將平的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他姐姐藤野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是菊裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 初次見面 我是冱木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 藤姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有個非常可愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 小將 你還有這樣的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級正統帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真叫人煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 芹香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？有客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹香小姐 車子洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼今天陪我去購物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下來還要修整下庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事晚點再做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不行 我正在修行途中…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是好男人 絕對要擒到手來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱熱鬧鬧的叫人羨慕才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家就我和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不想住在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子 頭髮該扒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是來看小肥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將平真不容易啊 各種方面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪你怎麼了 躲在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由美 內褲會被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 這次我一定要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪 冷靜下來 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你家這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒啥 其實我家有東西出沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西是指鬼怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 寺廟嘛 沒啥好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前可沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很平常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:06:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會編胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.56,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:07.84,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒欺負小咪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:08.76,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒欺負它…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點想回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說出沒 但也並不是就能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經習慣了就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打坐時有東西倒下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明沒有風 蠟燭卻自個熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修整好的庭院被弄得亂糟糟的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸都說「這也是佛門修行之一」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非小肥是看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不是因為佛事沒做夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.66,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼會出現鬼怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.37,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 寺廟和神社不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏沉眠著很多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀太郎大人 你察覺到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 微微感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這不是神社嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 這裏明明是寺廟！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這很久以前就在院落內了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是我家在管理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺廟裏有神社不是很常見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小真你很在意嗎 不愧是神社家孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前神明和佛祖都是交織在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼好稀奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神佛調和的餘音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們隨便看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 什麼又來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪 別怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀太郎 難道說這麼小的神社裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這和神社大小沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡惡作劇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 我們也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使又沒什麼稀奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺最近這事特別多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些東西都能倒下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 小風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了哦 小吹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗噗 小吹 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人呆呆的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是啊 小風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是 有些奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類竟然看得到我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那個奇怪的小不點是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 還有個大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們倆 給我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰小不點了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 那什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小風
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小吹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 銀 他們都被嚇著了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是還什麼都沒做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是因為他們這麼說我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是神使吧 沒和人類說過話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔你也是神使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們完全不一樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐貍呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們呀 是猴子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小風 就像爺爺之前說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我們以外還有很多各種各樣的神使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了沒 至今為止的騷動都是這倆幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏好像也沒人能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了吧 咱們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那怎麼行 既然如此得提醒他們別再惡作劇了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是外人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別多管閒事為好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你自己留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看見小風嗎 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 「可愛可愛」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類中的女性總是立馬就會這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小風就顧自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 小吹 可愛嗎可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快從悟身上滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什麼啊這蝴蝶結 真囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春的蝴蝶結
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀太郎 快給我抓住這只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後好好教訓教訓他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,論年紀 小春還算是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我說你們 適可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐貍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不服氣的話 就過來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打屁股 打屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沒那本事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然出門就不會遇到什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管神使還是人類 小孩子都一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 真琴 趕緊完事回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 大叔你好快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上 銀太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住好好教訓他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也別說別人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你們適可而止點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咪你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 討厭 你們正忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭了 哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天過的 什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 剛就是佛事用具倒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 將平 找不到小咪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是到墓地那塊去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去那邊找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 銀太郎 快抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺無所謂了 你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小風 那個拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 是風刮的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍 還能起風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這看來 可是能隨心所欲到處惡作劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的風 是那倆孩子刮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 人類能看見的話好難惡作劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙好礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 神使才不會做這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡作劇可好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我們忘掉煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你們不是要來抓我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大叔你扮鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春才沒那麼閒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手住手 你耍詐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來抓我們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 受夠了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 多事大笨女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:24.48,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你做這種小學生做的事要做到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 悟 那倆孩子為什麼要惡作劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是因為他們覺得好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們才沒考慮什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為惡作劇導致別人吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導致別人以為是鬼怪而害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是神使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果發生在小春你身上 你也不願意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實不願意…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是寺廟 沒人能看見他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們又是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是因為與人類的關係太疏遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去問問住持大師吧 或許能知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:16:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座神社現在是由我們家在管理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是早在建寺之前就在這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我們家寺廟佔用了這座神社的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是跟你說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前這一帶 經常會有猴子下山來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座神社的神使是神猿 想必也是因為如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神佛分離的那段時期
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為寺廟較大而且神社又沒人照料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就這樣留在了院落內
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 寺廟能發展成現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能也要多虧這座神社的保佑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子可是必勝的象徵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神明之猴 讀作神猿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 和佛祖一樣 都是我們應該感恩的神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去墓地那邊找找小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們去那邊找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前還有很多猴子來這裏玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是因為太孤單了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是因為想趕走人類才惡作劇的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前有很多同伴在 明明過得很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻因為寺廟的建立導致猴子們從這裏消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道啊 神使知曉過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說沒辦法 他們是孩子又沒人能看見他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春我也有討厭的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問問當事人如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼跑怎麼跑都立刻就被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不能告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 趕走人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從來沒這麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼還要惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 很沉悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來寺廟的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在哭泣 都很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 我們也會跟著傷感的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就想稍微嚇嚇他們 讓他們忘記憂傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 爺爺也說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前這裏的神使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說現已不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風 吹 就算同伴們不來了 但也無需哀嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是換成了人類罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說隨著人類增多會發生很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你們只要笑容以對就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是勝利象徵的神猿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不笑容滿面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就誰都不能獲得勝利的喜悅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們覺得應該快樂至上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 這裏有寺廟 也有墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們活的很久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要連同人類 同伴以及爺爺的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在以後的日子裏 也要一直默默守護這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 惡作劇或許是過了點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你們以你們的方式鼓舞了大家不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類也都有能夠自己排憂解難的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以別再惡作劇也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那多沒意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為嚇嚇人類好有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們最大的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 猴類的神使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了 冱木你真的很喜歡超自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很可愛啊 神明大人的惡作劇什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真吉利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好嗎 一兩隻猴靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家與之相似的也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在佛祖之餘 還能得到神明的佑護真叫人感激涕零
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真對那些傢伙不放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許應該偶爾來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們又沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將平他們家人也不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神使的事情 他們怎麼可能會相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不相信也沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定就是作為溝通雙方的橋樑而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小風和小吹完全不拘泥於神社或者寺廟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的神明大人真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也沒有比日本的神明大人更隨心所欲的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該說這是心胸寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,0:24:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為神明大人使者的神使
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅有狐貍 還有猴子 兔子 烏龜 烏鴉等等
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.29,0:24:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有著很多很多各種各樣的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.13,0:24:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類還真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.91,0:24:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願神明保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:55.79,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}私の生まれた　この場所この部屋で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.86,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}出会ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:06.34,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}古ぼけたランプは　今も優しい光を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:10.46,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.16,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ずっと昔から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:21.65,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}紡がれてきた時間を 気付かせてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:27.71,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}胸に灯そう　心の中のランプ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:32.47,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}今隠れてた絆照らし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:38.46,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}私にそっと　囁きかけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.10,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Ah 「僕はいつもここだよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:50.50,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}差し伸べた手ほら　繋いだら君に言おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:56.10,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}言葉は　「君を信じているから…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:02:01.46,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}この手を離さないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:55.79,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在這裏  我出生的這間小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.86,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}與你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:06.34,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那盞披滿灰塵的老煤油燈  現在依舊搖曳著溫暖的微光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:10.46,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}點亮我的心房
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.16,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}讓我回憶起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:21.65,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那段懵懂間悄然編織的青蔥歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:27.71,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那心靈的明燈  請照亮我的胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:32.47,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}如今也點亮了那深埋心底的絲絲羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:38.46,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}請悄悄地於我耳畔細語呢喃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.10,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Ah 「我一直陪伴在你身旁」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:50.50,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}伸出雙手 如果觸碰到你就可以對你訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:56.10,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那不變的話語 「因為相信你…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:02:01.46,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}請不要鬆開我的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:44.98,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}遠く聞こえてる　人の聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:51.44,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}振り返り　ほくそ笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:55.69,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}一から百になる刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:23:04.29,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}その一瞬が　永遠だね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:15.21,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}孤獨さえ支配したいと思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:26.29,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}疑心暗鬼　敵わないや　手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:38.45,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}世界の始まりは偽りの物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:45.35,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}月がそっと笑ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:50.96,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}なゆたの未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:55.65,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}繋ぐメッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:24:08.37,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕を空へ導いてくれるSTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:44.98,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}遠處傳來的 誰的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:51.44,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}回過頭去 暗自嬉笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:55.69,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}從一到百那霎那瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:23:04.29,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}也將是永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:15.21,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}原以為自己可以支配孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:26.29,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}但卻疑心暗鬼 果然敵不過 索性伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:38.45,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}世界的起始是個虛偽的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:45.35,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}月亮不禁一旁竊笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:50.96,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}這或許是連接
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:55.65,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那無盡歲月未來的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:24:08.37,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}指引我飛上天空的STORY

